				<guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/sky-rendering-1/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/skyrim-nightsky.webp&#34; width=&#34;900&#34;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;p&gt;The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/br&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/mordor-cloud.jpg&#34; width=&#34;900&#34;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;p&gt;The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/br&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/sunset-rdr2.jpg&#34; width=&#34;900&#34;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;p&gt;Red Dead Redemption 2&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;A star-filled night sky can captivate those who gaze upon it. Approaching storm clouds may embody a looming evil, while a brilliant sunset can leave a lasting impression. Weather shapes emotion and atmosphere, and the sky is an indispensable part of portraying it. In this article, we will explore the process of &lt;b&gt;physically based sky rendering&lt;/b&gt;.&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
